{"tid":1996092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法甲落實提早完季巴黎聖日耳門封王","createTime":"2020-04-30T17:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T07:04:50.000Z","uid":60658,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8db998a7742692ee3737a13bef43495619838d","tid":1996092,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】法國職業足球聯賽賽會正式宣布，今季法甲及法乙提早完結，巴黎聖日耳門成為今屆法甲冠軍。<br />\n賽會表示基於早前法國總理及政府的決定與聲明 ，宣布今季正式結束。<br />\n今屆法甲停賽之前，榜首的巴黎聖日耳門領先第二位的馬賽12分兼踢少一場，而提早完季之後，法甲基於場均得分定出最終排名，聖日耳門成為今屆冠軍。<br />\n賽會又決定「升二降二」，意味法甲最尾兩位的艾米恩斯及圖盧茲會降班。另外，羅連安特成為乙組冠軍，將連同第二位的朗斯一齊升班。"},{"pid":"05679857c8ccef16b1eac48f8025fea16eaf8b69","tid":1996092,"uid":83504,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"其實每一季都咁做就得"},{"pid":"df5e6a84d4326c5dc1be0b6a0cfb606e4e12b26e","tid":1996092,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:54:39.000Z","msg":"羅哥講波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7634c193bbf6caf3dbfa35a1d1fd68f41259d69e","tid":1996092,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"平常心jpg"},{"pid":"f881648ba6991b3862c09977a0da0242a791c92c","tid":1996092,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df5e6a84d4326c5dc1be0b6a0cfb606e4e12b26e","tid":1996092,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:54:39.000Z","msg":"羅哥講波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb8f5107a57106274c0b0d4a523f2092604b44f","tid":1996092,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7634c193bbf6caf3dbfa35a1d1fd68f41259d69e","tid":1996092,"uid":234509,"like":0,"